title: #185: Kiss the Cook (@ThisDavidTaylor)
itunes:title: Kiss the Cook with David Taylor
description: David Taylor met me at my LA AirBnb to talk about chefing. Chefing? Sure. David has been cooking for a few years now and he's gotten kind of into it. So we just talked about that. And of course, we meandered a crudload.
